Christopher H. Wright & Associates, P.C.



























 
At Christopher H. Wright & Associates, P.C., we are dedicated to providing effective legal representation to individuals and businesses alike. We offer our clients quality services for personal injury, property damage and other civil litigation  matters. This includes cases related to premises liability, products liability, contracts, subrogation, public utility, corporate liability and Pennsylvania One Call matters.Our firm is a member of the Better Business Bureau of Pennsylvania, and places a high priority on client satisfaction. We will be attentive and responsive to your needs throughout the legal process and work toward a resolution that satisfies your needs and goals.Since 1990, we have successfully represented clients in all phases of litigation, including discovery, motion practice, mediation, trial and appeals. Among our representative clients is a Fortune 50 company where we have served as outside defense counsel for more than 20 years.
 



To speak to an experienced attorney about your legal matter, contact us today, or send an on-line message using the form on this website. Our offices are conveniently located in Philadelphia and Malvern, PA.


